---

==============================================
                       Summary
==============================================

Cosmic Horizons is a highly ambitious space mod for Minecraft that aims to bring *true* planetary systems, realistic space travel, environments, etc., but it is early in development (alpha). Many features exist, especially around rendering, exploration, dimension generation, and tech blocks, but survival mode progression isn’t fully supported out of the box.  

Cosmic Unbound is an addon / complementary mod that bridges that gap: making survival mode viable by unlocking crafting / obtaining of space travel gear, adding content like planned space suits, etc.  

Together, they promise a path from early Minecraft survival through to full interplanetary exploration and technological progression.

